io.doov.core.dsl.impl

Class StringCondition

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.doov.core.dsl.impl.DefaultCondition<java.lang.String>
      • io.doov.core.dsl.impl.StringCondition
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Readable

    public class StringCondition
extends DefaultCondition<java.lang.String>
    Base class for string conditions.

    It contains a DslField to get the value from the model, a LeafMetadata to describe this node, and a BiFunction to take the value from the model and return an optional value.
